description: Check out these troops: army guy Tomas Petr and navy dude Jan Muzicka cruise each other in a park before making out and heading back home for even more fun and action. It's said that there's nothing like a man in uniform, but what happens where there are two? Let's find out as these two hunks do everything to each other!
title: Service Men Jan Muzicka and Tomas Petr Cruise for Sex
